Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:06.64,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:09.35,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:14.52,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:19.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:32.41,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:40.88,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.59,0:00:52.73,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:56.02,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:58.77,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.86,0:01:03.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:09.12,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:18.42,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:33.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:36.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be your boyfriend,\Nbut I can act like I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:39.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try hard\Nto make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:48.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have her meet L to find out\Nhis name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and eliminate the entire\Ntask force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill her afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the only person who knows\NKira's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let her live for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:04.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll just act like my boyfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:10.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, could you show me\Nyour Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's necessary\Nto make her trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you turn around?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a completely different type\Nof Shinigami from Rem, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know your name. Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:39.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:41.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:45.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Light, do you know\Nhow to kill a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:48.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already calling me\Nby my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could I call you "Knight" instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're like Misa's knight\Nin shining armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:03:00.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to check all\Nthe videos of Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the 22nd by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:03.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is very likely that Kira\Nand the Second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,made contact with each other there\Non that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Mr. Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:13.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:17.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like Mr. Mogi to keep\Nwatch over Light's activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light's activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:25.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the event that Light is Kira,\Nthe Second Kira might try to contact him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:26.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In some way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So when does Ryuzaki sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him sleeping in that\Nexact same position the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:40.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So when a Shinigami has feelings\Nfor a certain person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and kills someone in order to\Nextend that person's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Shinigami dies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine there's\Na Shinigami who would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:02.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It doesn't seem like\Nthe kind of thing that you would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, from where have you\Nbeen sending your tapes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to the television stations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:11.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... The first time was Osaka.\NThen it was Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This other time was from Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:17.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I used the Bullet Train so\Nmy location couldn't be pinpointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you still have videotapes\Nand envelopes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:22.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with your friend's fingerprints\Non them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:23.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should dispose of\Neverything used to create the videos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:33.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But only after sending one last video\Nfrom another location tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l will stop trying to meet Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd like to thank the police\Nfor their advice."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:46.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"But I'm going to help Kira\Nerase evil from the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:50.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to cooperate with him\Nand get his acceptance."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:56.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l will begin by punishing criminals\Nthat Kira hasn't punished yet. Also..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l plan to make this world\Na better place"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:04.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"by sharing this power\Namong those who are worthy."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Share the power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a line to throw off\Nthe investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already two people\Nwith this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too far of a stretch\Nthat there may be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they believe that they'll multiply,\Nit'll create a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to ask.\NJust tell me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:24.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, one more important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:27.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're caught by the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:36.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're arrested as a suspect,\Ndon't say anything about us or the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no proof against you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:40.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as they don't get\Na hold of the notebook and verify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you promise to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:47.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, we're officially boyfriend\Nand girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for my conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date with me\Nat least once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really doesn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like\Nyou'll understand unless I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L already suspects that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? L's pretty amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:16.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he doesn't understand or...\Nthat he's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's actually figured out\Nthat much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:23.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that,\NI've also been able to get close to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? L and Kira are\Nin contact with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:31.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both amazing.\NIt's making me kind of excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L thinks he's safe as long as\Nhe hides his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He came out and told me\Nhe was L in order to directly investigate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's only positive because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:47.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there isn't anyone else\Nwho could possibly be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:49.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I play it right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:53.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll trust me and\Nwe'll investigate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:58.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So all you have to do is\Ntake me to where L is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was difficult enough\Nfor me to get close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, if suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,someone close to me\Nsteps into the picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:12.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the actions of Kira and\Nthe Second Kira change...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that person will be suspected\Nof being the Second Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll end up casting\Nmore suspicion on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if we get together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:25.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he makes the connection\Nthat we're intimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand\Nwhat I'm trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:31.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of... So does that mean\Nwe can't go on dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't meet in public because\Nyou're afraid that he'll suspect you more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:35.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:39.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take some time\Nto think of a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:42.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you can see L without\Nletting him know you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:46.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need you\Nin order to eliminate L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to keep\Nin direct contact with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:50.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:51.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make sure that\Nour meetings don't stand out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:01.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean by that?\NYou're going to date other girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:04.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:10.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see you with another girl,\NI'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:11.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Misa sweetie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:15.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both risking our lives\Nto change the world, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:25.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...\NI love you more...than the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your feelings towards me\Nwere those of just a Kira admirer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:35.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only the first time we've met...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever experienced\Nlove at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:38.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:44.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, I wanted to meet Kira out of\Ngratitude and approval, not out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I first laid eyes on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this girl-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're popular as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:55.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if you love me,\Nyou'll obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me before that\Nyou didn't mind being used
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and just earlier, you insisted that\Nyou'd do as I say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:05.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't allow you to\Ndate other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:11.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have both notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't obey, I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:18.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that,\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:25.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to kill her,\NI'll write your name in my notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see her lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:37.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she dies before that date,\NI'll assume that you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:42.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you die if you\Nused your notebook to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Then you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:56.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Shinigami serious?\NThen that means, from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to have\Na girl stay out so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:10.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We ended up having\Na long conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mrs. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for staying so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:21.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, walk her to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be good to walk\Noutside with her now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:42.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. I was a bit worried at first,\Nbut she sure is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shinigami is going\Nto kill me if I kill the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:50.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I have to deal\Nwith her until she dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:57.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm forced to protect her so\Nshe doesn't get caught by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:04.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,\NLight really became my knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't kill him for real, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to kill a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that Shinigami has to use\Nthe Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to save a human's life that\Nit has fallen in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:36.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't kill Rem by using\Nthe Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to control someone to attack Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:45.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa 's put in danger,\NI'll be suspected first and be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, she's an even\Nbigger nuisance than L is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She...does something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.18,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz14.521\pos(379,240)\frx358\fry14}Misa Amane
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,visible like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:59.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen if it's discovered\Nthat I met with someone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! She's in the way no matter\Nhow I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do-?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:09.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Besides that, I should think\Nof a way to use Misa 's eyes to kill L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just eliminate L...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Light-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:18.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:23.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Sayu, could you keep Misa\Na secret from Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want you to keep it secret,\Nnot just from Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an up-and-coming model,\Nactually,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so it would be problematic\Nif people found out about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?! Is that so-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:44.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect for your girlfriend...\NI'll keep it a secret...for 5,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:45.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.61,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(329,52)}To-oh\NUniversity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:51.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On page 246...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's final message\Nwill arrive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of going to\Nthe television station,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it should be routed to\Nthe task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to headquarters\Nin order to see L's reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami... Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that you'd\Ngo out with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:16.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm sitting next\Nto you at this lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't seem happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been completely\Ninattentive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:28.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about the way\Neveryone's going to be talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:32.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I'm going out with Takada,\Nthe famous Miss To-oh University...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious,\Nyou really are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:43.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't think about such things.\NI don't like being called Miss whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:45.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this woman?\NShe actually likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:53.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Takada, let's just take\Nthings at our own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:54.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:13:59.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A video message from\Nthe Second Kira just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one? That's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think this is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not contact Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank the police\Nfor their advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:28.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to help Kira\Nerase evil from the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And gain his approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will begin by punishing criminals\Nthat Kira hasn't punished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I will share this power among\Nthose who are worthy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and make this world\Na better place by...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:48.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,makes me feel that Kira and\Nthe Second Kira have joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that\Nthey've joined forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you sense it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:58.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would\Nget the same impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:05.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, his attitude towards\Nmeeting Kira completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he now says that he wants\Nto punish criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that Kira didn't punish\Nin order to gain his approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he do this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably never thought\Nthat far, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's likely that he's working with\NKira and was told to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:29.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also ordered to hide\Nthe fact that they're working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That probably means that Kira\Nisn't thinking about his actions very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kira encounter something\Nhe couldn't overcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably was trying to scare us\Nby making it obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he'd recruited the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their union is really threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:52.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this lessens the suspicion\NI had of Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Ryuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light was Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then he wouldn't have sent\Nin a video like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:06.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He would have tried to threaten me, L,\Ninto appearing on television again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintaining that lie that\Nthey aren't working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:12.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he would have placed all\Nthe responsibility on Second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what he'd have him say:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"l stopped because\NKira told me to,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:23.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"but I don't think that warning\Nwould come from the real Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira should be happy if L died."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no way he'd stop me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never do that\Nif I were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:37.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:46.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L would never go on TV\Nno matter how he was threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't want to die\Nin someone else's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He would think of\Nsome way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:59.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, stop saying,\N"lf I were Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like hearing it,\Neven hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:03.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:08.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to tell Ryuzaki\Nwhat I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pose the scenario\Nhypothetically
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to solve this case quickly\Nand to clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:19.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's because\NI'm not Kira that I can talk in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:20.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:26.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it would be a problem\Nif you were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:30.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:33.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my first friend ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:46.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're a friend\NI have much in common with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lonely since you've been\Ntaking breaks from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to play tennis with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:12.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend-? Friend, huh?\NAren't you glad, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:14.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Ryuzaki immediately noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the connection between\NKira and the Second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to eliminate him quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes it all the more dangerous\Nfor me to see Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:32.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't wait\Ntwo weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to go\Nto your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:41.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is the first time\NI've really wanted to hit a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just wanted to see you\Nso badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Come over to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:01.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Misa! I saw you in\Na whole bunch of magazines-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:07.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, please get some tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:11.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Misa's ally, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:20.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've watched her many times\Nfrom the Shinigami Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:24.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've developed a bit of\Naffection for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Affection, even though\Nyou're a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:33.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to like that\NI said that I'd kill you if you tried to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:37.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that if\NMisa's happy that you'll feel fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:42.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to see her unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:49.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:51.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would my happiness\Nmake you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:01.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you ask Rem\Nto kill L?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem wants you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:09.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If L catches one of us,\Nwe'll both be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:16.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami can't tell a person's name\Nto someone who has a notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no restriction\Nagainst Rem killing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:25.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you kill L,\NI think I can love Misa more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I would be grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, it'll make us both happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:31.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:36.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Light to love me.\NLight and I will be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be...my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:51.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:57.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Light Yagami.\NI don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:01.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this ends up lengthening\Nyour lifespan, I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill L for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is a human who means\Nnothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:14.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:16.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L will die,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:29.46,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:34.84,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:43.85,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:50.27,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:54.82,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:22:00.53,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:08.00,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:13.17,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:23.85,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:29.19,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:39.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Since Ryuga's revealed\Nthat he's L, I must kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a wager now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:46.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will be L's,\Nno Ryuga/Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:47.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...date of death.
